            Like the noble Lord, I rather think that the impact of money that will come to children born after 1 September 2002&#x2014;they presumably do not have a vote in any 2005 election&#x2014;and that will come to them only in 2020 is not much of an electoral bribe. In those circumstances, cynicism is misplaced.
